high_descs: Turn left, hang a left at the table and walk to the red couch on the left.
Pick up the red credit card from the left cushion on the couch.
Turn right and walk to the right side of the couch to your left.
Put the credit card inside the cardboard box on the right couch cushion.
Pick up the cardboard box with the credit card inside on the couch.
Turn around, hang a left at the red ottoman and walk to the round table next to the television.
Put the box with the credit card inside on top of the round table.
anns.task_desc: Place a box with a card on a table.

high_descs: Turn left and walk towards the wall, then hang a left and walk over to the red couch.
Pick up the red credit card off of the couch cushion.
Turn right and walk forward then turn left to face the couch.
Put the red credit card in the cardboard box on the couch.
Pick up the cardboard box with the credit card in it off of the couch.
Walk over to the small black table next to the television behind you.
Put the cardboard box with the credit card in it on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a cardboard box with a credit card in it on a round black table.

high_descs: Go to the sofa
Pick up the credit card from the sofa
Go to the box on the sofa
Place the credit card in the box
Pick up the box
Go to the round black table
Place the box on the round black table
anns.task_desc: Move a box and keys from a sofa to a table
